'''干涉合成孔径雷达'''（{{Lang-en|'''In'''terferometric '''s'''ynthetic '''a'''perture '''r'''adar}}，縮寫：'''InSAR'''或'''IfSAR'''）是一种应用于[[测绘|测绘]]和[[遥感|遥感]]的[[雷达|雷达]]技术。这种测量方法使用两幅或多幅[[合成孔径雷达|合成孔径雷达]]影像图，根据卫星或飞机接收到的回波的[[相位|相位]]差来生成[[数字高程模型|数字高程模型]]或者地表形变图。<ref>{{Citation|last=Massonnet |first=D. |last2=Feigl |first2=K. L. |year=1998 |title=Radar interferometry and its application to changes in the earth’s surface |periodical=Rev. Geophys. |volume=36 |issue=4 |pages=441–500|doi=10.1029/97RG03139}}</ref><ref>{{Citation|last=Burgmann |first=R. |last2=Rosen |first2=P.A. |last3=Fielding |first3=E.J. |year=2000 |title=Synthetic aperture radar interferometry to measure Earth's surface topography and its deformation |periodical=Annual Review of Earth and Planetary Sciences |volume=28 |pages=169–209|doi=10.1146/annurev.earth.28.1.169}}</ref><ref>{{Citation |last =Hanssen |first =Ramon F. |year =2001 |title =Radar Interferometry: Data Interpretation and Error Analysis |publisher =Kluwer Academic |isbn = 9780792369455}}</ref>理论上此技术可以测量数日或数年间厘米级的地表形变，可以用于自然灾害监测，例如地震、火山和滑坡，以及结构工程尤其是沉降监测和结构稳定性。

