=== 构造 ===
InSAR可应用于[[地质构造|构造]]形变，例如地震造成的地表位移。首次应用实在1992年[[Landers|Landers]]地震<ref name="Massonnet93">{{Citation|last=Massonnet |first=D. |last2=Rossi |first2=M. |last3=Carmona |first3=C. |last4=Adragna |first4=F. |last5=Peltzer |first5=G. |last6=Feigl |first6=K. |last7=Rabaute |first7=T. |year=1993 |title=The displacement field of the Landers earthquake mapped by radar interferometry |periodical=Nature |volume=364 |issue= |pages=138–142|doi=10.1038/364138a0}}</ref>，很快便在全球各种地震之中普遍使用，特别是对1999年土耳其[[伊兹密特|伊兹密特]]和[[2003年巴姆大地震|2003年伊朗巴姆地震]]进行了深入研究。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.esa.int/esaEO/SEMLD1W4QWD_index_0.html|title=Envisat's rainbow vision detects ground moving at pace fingernails grow|date=August 6, 2004|accessdate=2007-03-22|publisher=European Space Agency|archive-date=2007-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070412141241/http://www.esa.int/esaEO/SEMLD1W4QWD_index_0.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{cite web|url=http://earth.esa.int/ers/article_archive/izmit_1999.html|title=The Izmit Earthquake of 17 August 1999 in Turkey|accessdate=2007-03-22|publisher=European Space Agency|archive-date=2007-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070310091234/http://earth.esa.int/ers/article_archive/izmit_1999.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> InSAR也可用于监测[[断层|断层]]。

=== 火山监测 ===
InSAR被用于各种[[火山|火山]]监测，包括爆发造成的形变，爆发中深层岩浆分布的变化造成的地表应变，火山体的重力延展，和火山构造形变信号。<ref>{{Citation|last=Wadge |first=G. |year=2003 |title=A strategy for the observation of volcanism on Earth from space |periodical=Phil. Trans. Royal Soc.Lond. |volume=361 |pages=145–156 }}</ref>早期基于InSAR的火山研究对象包括[[埃特纳火山|埃特纳火山]],<ref name="Massonnet95">{{Citation|last=Massonnet |first=D. |last2=Briole |first2=P. |last3=Arnaud |first3=A. |year=1995 |title=Deflation of Mount Etna monitored by spaceborne radar interferometry |periodical=Nature |volume=375 |pages=567–570|doi=10.1038/375567a0 }}</ref>和[[基拉韋厄峰|基拉韋厄峰]]，<ref>{{Citation|last=Rosen |first=P. A. |last2=Hensley |first2=S. |last3=Zebker |first3=H. A. |last4=Webb |first4=F. H. |last5=Fielding |first5=E. J. |year=1996 |title=Surface deformation and coherence measurements of Kilauea Volcano, Hawaii, from SIR C radar interferometry |periodical=J. Geophys. Res. |volume=101 |issue=E10 |pages=23,109–23,126|doi=10.1029/96JE01459 }}</ref>随着此领域的发展，更多的火山研究开始进行。尽管此技术作为可行的火山监测技术存在各种限制，例如卫星的重现时间、档案数据的缺乏、相干性和大气误差，但它仍然广泛应用于火山形变的学术研究。<ref>{{Citation|last=Stevens |first=N.F. |last2=Wadge |first2=G. |year=2004 |title=Towards operational repeat-pass SAR interferometry at active volcanoes |periodical=Natural Hazards |volume=33  |pages=47–76|doi=10.1023/B:NHAZ.0000035005.45346.2b }}</ref>最近，InSAR也被应用于[[埃塞俄比亚|埃塞俄比亚]]的[[峡谷|峡谷]]研究。<ref>{{Citation |last=Wright |first=T.J. |last2=Ebinger |first2=C. |last3=Biggs |first3=J. |last4=Ayele |first4=A. |last5=Yirgu |first5=G. |last6=Keir |first6=D. |last7=Stork |first7=A. |year=2006 |title=Magma-maintained rift segmentation at continental rupture in the 2005 Afar dyking episode |periodical=Nature |volume=442 |pages=291–294 |doi=10.1038/nature04978 |url=http://earth.leeds.ac.uk/~eartjw/papers/Wright_Afar_Nature2006.pdf |accessdate=2009-07-13 |archive-date=2007-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070104110955/http://earth.leeds.ac.uk/%7Eeartjw/papers/Wright_Afar_Nature2006.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

